attributes.Long form description: The student needs to disassemble the table, so he unscrews all the hex socket heads of the table very slightly with the Allen wrench, then he unscrews all the hex socket heads faster completely with his hands. He disassembles the middle shelf and all the legs one by one, after all of these steps the student finally disassembles the top table and he finishes the task.

attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble the bedside table from IKEA, please go ahead and disassemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the hex socket heads from the upper tray slightly.
The student unscrews the hex socket heads from the lower tray slightly.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the Allen wrench.
The student drops the Allen wrench.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the lower tray.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Student should not drop the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the legs from the table and upper tray.

attributes.Transcription: The job ended. You can now press stop.
